<Layout
  title="AIO Liquid Cooler Power Consumption: Pump Headers & Wiring — PSUCheck"
  description="Learn about the power requirements of All-in-One (AIO) liquid coolers. Understand pump amp limits, SATA power cables, and motherboard headers."
  schema={faqSchema}
>
  <article class="guide-article">
